    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>纯粹的畅快体验，飙升的肾上腺素！</strong> <br><strong>LEGENDS BMX</strong> 是一款令人精神振奋、心旷神怡的极限运动游戏，专为极限运动迷打造！骑上你的小轮车，驰骋于多个公园和场景之中，完成让人叹为观止的花式动作。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291690/extras/472e06f391878c25c220b93091001b0f.poster.avif?t=1742634925\" width=720 height=405 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291690/extras/472e06f391878c25c220b93091001b0f.webm?t=1742634925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>简洁 &amp; 直观</u></strong> <br>通过简洁易上手的机制和直观的控制，享受无限乐趣与丰富体验。飞跃坡道和垂直面，秀出震撼技巧，达成目标分数。在类真实环境中，探索多个公园，场景中有丰富的坡道、地面和竖直面。追求卓越，登顶排行榜！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>尽情骑行 &amp; 挑战自我</u></strong> <br>自由骑行，在多个公园和场景中完成路线、秀出操作，轻松积攒高分。尝试最疯狂的动作特技，独特的单向操作系统将助你一臂之力。在完成第一个特技后，你的特技连线就开始了，每个额外的特技和组合都有奖励，带来不断增加额外的分数，直到骑手摔倒或停止。特技连线的总分数随后会被加到你的总分中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291690/extras/dbc7829acd7ea319f74673b0b36eda1a.poster.avif?t=1742634925\" width=720 height=405 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291690/extras/dbc7829acd7ea319f74673b0b36eda1a.webm?t=1742634925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>专注竞赛 &amp; 个性定制</u></strong> <br>展现数十种特技，涵盖转把、空翻、后轮滑、各种前后炮等多种变化。挑战最佳成绩，冲击全球排行榜。挑选自己喜爱的骑手与自行车，每个都有其独特的风格与节奏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291690/extras/2994e62ab103cbefa1b17fdb2530c519.poster.avif?t=1742634925\" width=720 height=405 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291690/extras/2994e62ab103cbefa1b17fdb2530c519.webm?t=1742634925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>卡通 &amp; 写实风格兼具</u></strong> <br>LEGENDS BMX 将独特的 3D 卡通风格与类真实公园、沉浸式环境和酷炫视觉效果完美融合。动态等距镜头紧随骑手，增强了骑行、流畅运动和特技动作的刺激感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>游戏体验反馈</u></strong> <br>为了增强游戏体验，LEGENDS BMX 加入了精彩的视觉效果，包括行车特效、前后炮火花、刹车痕迹、尘土飞扬、摄像机效果、粒子特效和泵道轨迹等。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
